name: Zillow Home Value Index (Zip): Median Listing Price - Three Bedrooms - 90210, Beverly Hills, CA
description: The Zillow Home Value Index is Zillow's estimate of the median market value of median listing price - three bedrooms within the zip of 90210, Beverly Hills, CA. This data is calculated by Zillow Real Estate Research (www.zillow.com/research) using their database of 110 million homes.
